Air Warlock
An elemental mage attuned to air and lightning, commanding winds, calling storms,
and hurling bolts of elemental energy. Air Warlocks draw PPE from ley lines and
the open sky, and are feared wherever weather and magic intersect on Rifts Earth.

Starting skills: Lore magic, wilderness survival, meditation, holistic medicine,
plus elective picks from Technical, Lore, and Physical categories.

Attribute requirements: ME 12.
Starting equipment: Light robes or travelling clothes, focus crystal attuned
to air, spellbook of elemental invocations, and a concealed sidearm.
Starting credits: 500 credits (standard kit).
PPE / ISP: Base PPE 35, +8 per level. No starting ISP.

